blog.name: bokunoreversebang
blog.title: Boku no Reverse Bang
blog.description: Hi, there! You're on the site dedicated to the Reverse Bang Challenge. Instead of traditional order of any bang, we ask for arts and give them to writers to creat a story based on it. You can join with any ship you like or without ship at all. Our theme is SWITCH. We'll be happy to have you on board!

title: Theme
body:
For the Revers Bang, we’re using the theme: 

SWITCH

We hope it’ll inspire you to create amazing arts and great stories. 

Credits: @silhouettart

Tips about the theme

It’s can be understand as a simple hair color flip, clothes swap, as well as a journey through dimensions and time. The possibilities are endless and you can choose any of them. If you’re not sure that your idea suits our requirements, feel free to ask us.

We’ll be glad if you use the theme, but if you still want to participate and the theme isn’t to your liking, you can also skip it. It’s a very welcomed suggestion, but you’re not obligated to use it, if you’ve got a better idea which suits your heart content more than the theme.

blog.description: Has the godforsaken grape been smashed yet? Find out here as we count down the days until we celebrate with the finest of wine for the sweetest of victories.

summary: i respect you and your blog, like even though i love mineta and  do not want him dead, i respect your opinion and the way you're...
question: i respect you and your blog, like even though i love mineta and  do not want him dead, i respect your opinion and the way you're going about this, like i haven't once seen you attack a mineta fan, you just explain why you hate mineta and want him dead, and use this as a place to let off steam and i think that's admirable.
answer: thank you! i hope everyone understand that too, that this blog is to bash on the character. the only times where its directed at the people is when they come here and yell at me or diminish the feelings of those hurt by mineta. but generally speaking, as long as mineta’s flaws are recognized by his fans, then there’s literally no hard feelings here.

summary: Boku no Hero Academia Merch Preview! Here are some things I picked up after speaking to you guys last week! >> Animate Cafe...
caption:
Boku no Hero Academia Merch Preview!

Here are some things I picked up after speaking to you guys last week!

>> Animate Cafe Acrylic Keychain Stands 

I had to get a few samples to calm my acrylic PTSD hahaha~ My friend says they all look good. These babies are about 6cm tall. 

>> Ichiban Kuji comic text set - Aizawa, special Midoriya, All Might

  • Aizawa is on the low stock side so I got a few just in case. All Might I just wanted to see what he looks like irl haha~ (his ichiban kuji orange tan continues :’))
  • The special Midoriya’s 100% Smash effect is printed on. So again, I had to get these last few good ones asap! 8D

Full selection of characters from both sets will be available to order via the April Group Order. 

Web Shop News

Wok on the new web shop interface continues! 

I have finished adding the products from several series, so maybe I will invite you guys to a ~test visit later this week. You can browse those series, put things in cart, try the check out process. See if things work smoothly. :)
